{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "DVLA - to add a new category for vehicle classification - to add, Campervan",
        "additional_details": "We recently bought and Campervan and sent off for the reclassification and was rejected due to it looking like a van - it\u2019s hardly your everyday van!\r\n\r\nApppreciate that the police need to be able to identify a vehicle if stolen but a van with side windows it is not.\r\n\r\nMany Campervan\u2019s have pop top roofs bike racks and are styled - therefore relating to nothing that a van with windows would look like - oh and they also have a kitchen, bed etc.",
        "background": "DVLA have recently changed the classification of a Campervan conversion which used to be under  the classification of Motorhome, now all Campervan\u2019s are being rejected and classified as a van with side windows - this is unacceptable and deserves the right to to have its own classification.",
